kun reading compounds: 鱈【たら】gadid (any fish of the family Gadidae, incl. cod, haddock, whiting and pollack), Pacific cod (Gadus macrocephalus)
鱈子【たらこ】cod roe (roe of any fish from family Gadidae, esp. salted walleye pollack roe)

チーズ鱈【チーズたら】cheese tara, stick of cheese sandwiched between two thin strips of dried fish paste
